--- SCENARIO: open draft (default public mode) ---
# Players register from the group without opening a private chat with the bot, so
# the bot cannot DM them. Every pick pool is therefore posted publicly as a
# generated image in the group with no buttons, and each registration carries a
# "start a private chat" warning. No DMs are sent — this mirrors live behavior.

--- CHAT ---
alice: /lobby
ambotorix: Lobby created by alice
bob: /register
ambotorix: Player bob added to lobby*       # * = the "start a private chat" DM warning
carol: /register
ambotorix: Player carol added to lobby*

--- CHAT ---
alice: /start
ambotorix: Slot order: 1. {player} 2. {player} 3. {player}
ambotorix: Map: {map}
ambotorix: alice:
ambotorix: <image>          # alice's pick pool, posted publicly as a generated image
ambotorix: bob:
ambotorix: <image>
ambotorix: carol:
ambotorix: <image>

--- DM (alice) ---
ambotorix:        # nothing — alice never opened a private chat, so no DM is delivered

--- DM (bob) ---
ambotorix:

--- DM (carol) ---
ambotorix:
